::Killer/Prowl/DevilDuer::

"Wait up!" Killer yells, limping/hopping toward Anubis and Hades. The fall 
had nearly destroyed his left leg, making it hard for him to walk.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The missile hits Prowl in the side, sending the maximal flying to the ground, 
his side shooting sparks.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer walks up to Nemesis, looking down at the unconscious bot. He 
himself was in near-perfect shape, having only fired of one shot in the whole 
battle. He chuckles, grabbing Nemesis and lifting the bot to his shoulders, 
running off toward the Alliance base.
